look at these pictures.

41
00:04:27,147 --> 00:04:29,937
Thank you for coming into my life.

42
00:04:50,707 --> 00:04:51,707
I didn't realize it.

43
00:04:52,757 --> 00:04:53,667
Lee Sina…

44
00:04:54,007 --> 00:04:55,637
Until I fell in love with her,

45
00:04:57,137 --> 00:04:58,717
I didn't realize my hatred toward you…

46
00:05:01,057 --> 00:05:02,227
was gone.

47
