-My first love.

115
00:11:29,567 --> 00:11:31,317
Oh! Yes.

116
00:11:31,407 --> 00:11:33,447
Can you still root for me even now?

117
00:11:34,027 --> 00:11:34,947
Of course.

118
00:11:45,457 --> 00:11:46,747
My first love…

119
00:11:49,667 --> 00:11:51,087
is Mr. Noh Gojin.

120
00:11:52,547 --> 00:11:55,677
My first love
who I waited desperately for 12 years

121
00:11:57,217 --> 00:11:58,717
is him.

122
00:12:01,517 --> 00:12:02,687
I know

123
00:12:03,187 --> 00:12:05,517
that Mr. Noh is
pretending to have amnesia.

124
00:12:06,897 --> 00:12:09,027
He's taking revenge on me
because he misunderstood

125
00:12:09,647 --> 00:12:11,607
that I abandoned him.

126
00:12:12,197 --> 00:12:14,317
That's why he needed a fake fiancée too.

127
00:12:16,827 --> 00:12:17,787
Gojin…

128
00:12:18,867 --> 00:12:20,327
still loves me.

129
00:12:22,407 --> 00:12:24,827
So please end things from your end.

130
00:12:40,557 --> 00:12:44,057
Gojin still loves me.

131
00:12:45,727 --> 00:12:48,067
So please end things from your end.

132
00:13:42,157 --> 00:13:43,157
Gojin!

133
00:13:43,287 --> 00:13:44,287
Hello.

134
00:13:48,287 --> 00:13:49,207
Where are you going?

135
00:13:49,287 --> 00:13:50,377
To a convenience store.

136
00:13:51,127 --> 00:13:53,457
Oh, by the way,

137
00:13:54,417 --> 00:13:55,877
can I come hang out at your place?

138
00:13:56,467 --> 00:13:57,337
What?

139
00:13:58,717 --> 00:14:00,177
Sure… Come over.

140
00:14:00,257 --> 00:14:01,507
Yes!

141
00:14:02,717 --> 00:14:05,677
-Your sister is home, right?
-No. She left already.

142
00:14:06,267 --> 00:14:08,097
She already left for work?

143
00:14:08,187 --> 00:14:09,057
Yes.

144
00:14:09,727 --> 00:14:10,727
What's with her?

145
00:14:11,817 --> 00:14:13,067
Did she go without me?

146
00:14:14,437 --> 00:14:16,897
Oh, right. She must've gone ahead

147
00:14:16,987 --> 00:14:18,357
feeling embarrassed to be hungover.

148
00:14:18,607 --> 00:14:20,657
-She drank?
-I saw her

149
00:14:20,737 --> 00:14:23,287
drinking with a stunning woman
at a food stall last night.

150
00:14:52,857 --> 00:14:54,067
Why did you want to see me?

151
00:14:54,897 --> 00:14:58,397
I thought we finished
our discussion last night.

152
00:15:00,277 --> 00:15:03,697
I realized something
after thinking all night.

153
00:15:04,947 --> 00:15:05,787
What is it?

154
00:15:06,497 --> 00:15:10,497
How much I like Noh Gojin.

155
00:15:12,837 --> 00:15:13,667
So what?

156
00:15:13,747 --> 00:15:18,087
I'm going to continue to stay by Mr. Noh.

157
00:15:21,587 --> 00:15:23,847
You'll be the one
who will get hurt in the end.

158
00:15:24,347 --> 00:15:27,137
Because Gojin will
come back to me after all.

159
00:15:29,477 --> 00:15:32,477
I'll ask Mr. Noh directly how he feels.

160
00:15:37,067 --> 00:15:39,237
Being misdiagnosed taught me something.

161
00:15:40,647 --> 00:15:44,657
I need to follow my heart
this very moment and live my life.

162
00:15:47,827 --> 00:15:48,947
I'm going to

163
00:15:50,367 --> 00:15:52,207
keep loving Mr. Noh.

164
00:15:55,377 --> 00:15:56,417
What is it that you want?

165
00:15:57,667 --> 00:15:59,757
Money? Or becoming an instructor?

166
00:16:01,257 --> 00:16:02,627
I can give you everything you want.

167
00:16:06,387 --> 00:16:08,677
No, I don't need all that.

168
00:16:11,057 --> 00:16:13,597
Do you think you're my match?

169
00:16:17,357 --> 00:16:21,357
You can never beat me, Ms. Lee Sina.

170
00:16:42,507 --> 00:16:43,627
I'm going to

171
00:16:44,837 --> 00:16:46,597
keep loving Mr. Noh.

172
00:17:03,487 --> 00:17:06,867
Ms. Lee Sina isn't as good
at keeping a secret as I thought.

173
00:17:09,537 --> 00:17:10,537
What?

174
00:17:11,037 --> 00:17:12,957
Are you worried that I was mean to her?

175
00:17:13,037 --> 00:17:16,207
Don't get her involved in our problem.
She has nothing to do with it.

176
00:17:17,247 --> 00:17:18,287
I came to tell you that.

177
00:17:24,467 --> 00:17:26,757
You always make me miserable.

178
00:17:28,047 --> 00:17:31,387
I waited for 12 years to protect you.
12 long years!

179
00:17:32,427 --> 00:17:35,597
How can you tell me
you love another woman?

180
00:17:36,847 --> 00:17:39,017
How can you do that
when you don't even have amnesia?

181
00:17:41,527 --> 00:17:43,027
Are you doing this on purpose

182
00:17:43,817 --> 00:17:45,357
to take revenge on me?

183
00:17:47,697 --> 00:17:49,277
Please don't do this.

184
00:17:52,617 --> 00:17:53,947
I'm not taking revenge.

185
00:17:55,287 --> 00:17:56,247
I don't

186
00:17:57,247 --> 00:17:58,167
hate you anymore.

187
00:17:59,327 --> 00:18:00,167
Because…

188
00:18:02,377 --> 00:18:06,717
even at this very moment,
I'm worried about her.

189
00:18:08,137 --> 00:18:09,757
I don't want her
to get hurt because of me.

190
00:18:11,967 --> 00:18:14,677
I'm the one
who got hurt now because of you.

191
00:18:15,267 --> 00:18:16,807
It's me,

192
00:18:17,387 --> 00:18:18,897
not Lee Sina!

193
00:18:19,647 --> 00:18:21,397
It's all in the past now.

194
00:18:23,357 --> 00:18:25,067
You'll be fine soon.

195
00:18:37,077 --> 00:18:39,367
"I'll be fine"?

196
00:19:20,827 --> 00:19:23,747
Sir, the research team meeting
is in ten minutes.

197
00:19:26,127 --> 00:19:27,257
Let's just…

198
00:19:31,007 --> 00:19:32,637
skip work today.

199
00:19:37,387 --> 00:19:40,437
Are you upset
that I came to work ahead of you?

200
00:19:41,517 --> 00:19:42,517
No.

201
00:19:43,647 --> 00:19:46,107
Then, is something wrong?

202
00:19:48,527 --> 00:19:50,567
What did you do with the ring?

203
00:19:51,607 --> 00:19:53,907
Oh. I took it off.

204
00:19:54,567 --> 00:19:55,407
Why?

205
00:19:56,697 --> 00:19:58,657
Because it's a fake engagement ring.

206
00:20:07,167 --> 00:20:08,797
We aren't a fake couple anymore.

207
00:20:12,427 --> 00:20:15,217
You met with Ms. Baek, right?

208
00:20:17,007 --> 00:20:18,927
How did you know?

209
00:20:21,727 --> 00:20:25,727
Why don't you ask me
what my relationship with Ms. Baek is?

210
00:20:26,937 --> 00:20:28,937
Why don't you get upset
that I didn't tell you?

211
00:20:29,897 --> 00:20:31,067
Are you holding it in again?

212
00:20:33,357 --> 00:20:34,737
I don't hold things in anymore.

213
00:20:34,817 --> 00:20:36,447
Then why don't you say something?

214
00:20:38,287 --> 00:20:41,707
It seems like you need some time.

215
00:20:44,037 --> 00:20:45,417
Someone said to me once

216
00:20:46,167 --> 00:20:48,497
that it takes time to break up too,

217
00:20:49,247 --> 00:20:52,087
not just to fall in love.

218
00:21:05,307 --> 00:21:07,897
I hated and resented her for a long time.

219
00:21:09,267 --> 00:21:10,977
I could only feel my broken heart.

220
00:21:13,147 --> 00:21:14,647
If I didn't have you,

221
00:21:15,407 --> 00:21:17,987
I'd still be living that way like a fool.

222
00:21:25,207 --> 00:21:26,497
I was afraid

223
00:21:26,577 --> 00:21:28,207
that you might hold it in again.

224
00:21:32,707 --> 00:21:33,717
It's okay

225
00:21:34,007 --> 00:21:36,047
because I won't tell you
about my first love either.

226
00:21:39,507 --> 00:21:40,757
You can't do that.

227
00:21:42,807 --> 00:21:44,227
Why not? It's up to me.

228
00:21:44,807 --> 00:21:46,187
Gosh, how dare you.

229
00:21:46,437 --> 00:21:47,437
Who was it?

230
00:21:48,857 --> 00:21:49,857
Who was it?

231
00:21:50,227 --> 00:21:51,897
It's not like you'd know
even if I told you.

232
00:21:51,977 --> 00:21:53,147
Maybe I do.

233
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:54,357
I doubt it.

234
00:21:54,437 --> 00:21:56,817
When? What was it like?

235
00:21:56,907 --> 00:21:58,907
-What?
-What was it like?

236
00:22:10,537 --> 00:22:13,167
You got the exams? When can you send them?

237
00:22:14,837 --> 00:22:17,467
Okay. I'll transfer the balance
as soon as I get them.

238
00:22:17,877 --> 00:22:19,507
Yes, I will.

239
00:22:23,557 --> 00:22:26,847
Now I'll go big
as soon as I do a live broadcast

240
00:22:26,937 --> 00:22:28,307
with the expected questions.

241
00:22:28,977 --> 00:22:30,897
What? "The rising sun"?

242
00:22:31,767 --> 00:22:35,777
Shin Jinyoung, that rookie,
is no match for me!

243
00:22:36,817 --> 00:22:37,987
What did you say?

244
00:22:39,987 --> 00:22:40,987
Hey, there.

245
00:22:42,327 --> 00:22:43,367
I said it digested well.

246
00:22:49,827 --> 00:22:51,997
I'm filming a video log today,

247
00:22:52,087 --> 00:22:54,497
but my face looks so gloomy.

248
00:22:54,587 --> 00:22:56,877
Should I borrow
a mini lighting equipment from Mr. Gong?

249
00:22:56,967 --> 00:22:58,047
But he went to Baek Edu.

250
00:22:58,127 --> 00:22:59,377
Oh, right.

251
00:22:59,467 --> 00:23:02,677
Absence makes the heart grow fonder.

252
00:23:04,307 --> 00:23:07,677
I feel his absence now that he's gone
even though he was so obnoxious.

253
00:23:07,767 --> 00:23:09,137
You're right.

254
00:23:19,607 --> 00:23:22,487
It's me, Michelle Lee. Nice to see you--

255
00:23:25,037 --> 00:23:26,237
Gosh, seriously.

256
00:23:33,917 --> 00:23:36,047
Ms. Ma, did you borrow from a loan shark?

257
00:23:38,007 --> 00:23:39,927
This fell out of your diary.

258
00:23:41,177 --> 00:23:42,587
What do you mean, a loan shark?

259
00:23:43,177 --> 00:23:45,097
It was on the ground
in front of the office,

260
00:23:45,427 --> 00:23:46,717
so I just picked up the garbage.

261
00:23:47,767 --> 00:23:49,387
I see.

262
00:23:50,387 --> 00:23:54,397
If you need money, just tell me.

263
00:24:00,487 --> 00:24:01,947
Hey, Lee Mikyung!

264
00:24:04,617 --> 00:24:05,867
Don't you know who I am?

265
00:24:07,617 --> 00:24:09,407
I'm senior to you.

266
00:24:10,037 --> 00:24:11,577
